Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從這裡開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:00:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩 要加油咯!

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}マジックナンバー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:11.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:11.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:27.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:27.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:30.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:30.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:35.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:35.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:43.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:43.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:54.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:54.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:56.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:02:00.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:02:00.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:10.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:10.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:17.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:17.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:21.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:21.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...祈願少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來到這裡了 人類所居住的人間界你清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我非常清楚!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據你在這裡的努力情況決定你的願望是否能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 當然知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一到這裡就要鑽到這種地方來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不過 我覺得這樣藏起來說話比較有神秘感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說比較好玩吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼高興有什麼用啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花戶小鳩!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想去的地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個那傢伙告訴你需要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須用[瓶]裝滿受傷的心靈!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須先獲得[瓶]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獲得[瓶]要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能在這裡生活的測試必須合格!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯!今天一整天要考核你是否有在人間界生活的常識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試已經開始了 在本大人的監視and審判之下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底懂沒懂啊 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試要判定你能夠遵守這裡的常識行動到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來試試看吧 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做與這春天的公園相適應的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去做!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?五百祗先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是春天還悶頭大睡的蓑蟲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎...真是的 連在公園裡自然地行動都不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真是的 為什麼沒有把垃圾拿出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要趕不上巴士了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要遲到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟掉了一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔!來得正好 接下來的測試...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你如何處理這垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾丟棄處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾丟棄處在哪兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(盡量減少垃圾)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 烏鴉先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在盯著垃圾的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點的話可是要被啄的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯著...烏鴉先生盯著垃圾...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉先生!請!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把烏鴉招引過來你到底打算做什麼?啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏鴉先生麼看上去很餓的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那不是也寫著盡量減少垃圾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪是什麼小鳩 叫你土鳩就足夠了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就一個人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去喝茶麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道在這附近有一家很不錯的店喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 大白天就出來搭訕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們請客啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請客?真是太感謝你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!真是太好了啊 五百祗先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼到這裡的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 人家請客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡受傷了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 剛才對我們做了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 可不要小看我們啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來帶著男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人搭兩句訕就飄起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?我才沒有飄起來呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你笑的那麼燦爛 也難怪人家會那麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好今天天這麼晴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來賞花的客人很多 要忙起來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 籐本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個真是非常可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這個盤子給撤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 去打聽一下他叫什麼名字怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼不好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡啊 籐本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微笑一笑的話肯定會大受歡迎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了 不受歡迎也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個討厭的傢伙呢 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 忘記關了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(艾草保育園)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是籐本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 清花老師

Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙又來保育園了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 我馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 店長 我有點急事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事呢 有好多人呢 五百祗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是賞花會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 聞起來很好吃的樣子 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呢 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐 幫忙撿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎麼了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來人手就不夠...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了表示歉意 讓我幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加一瓶啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 剛好打工的人突然回去了 幫大忙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 能幫上忙我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於小鳩來說這還真是少見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這邊的火鍋還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 能幫我們煮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鍋...我煮...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也可以當測驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下吧 小鳩會怎樣煮火鍋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水還沒有煮開 不可以直接放啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊 肉先不能放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你放牛奶幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?但是牛奶很有營養...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要放巧克力啊?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過甜食會很精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊 不要放納豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得看起來有點像地獄的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但...但是別浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆你也吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 這個就當做我們店的招牌料理了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你這麼年輕 還挺能幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我搞得也想嘗嘗看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個土鳩居然這麼囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的小鳩關於火鍋的常識是0分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 結果還是做出來像樣的火鍋了 就40分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚 怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖 看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼哄都還是哭個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小姐你的錯哦 請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子晚上總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不給鄰居們添麻煩 我經常帶他來這個公園
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不哭到累絕對不肯睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前媽媽總是在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一哭就給他唱歌 他就不哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他媽媽...現在...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間正在為了他努力工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我得好好地照顧他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是婆婆我的歌聲沒法哄他不哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我唱一唱試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我為這個孩子唱唱歌試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我可能沒他的媽媽唱得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...會全力唱好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}春に咲く花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}夏広がる空よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}心の中に刻まれて煌く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}朝に降る雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}窓を閉ざす日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}胸にあふれる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}光は雲の上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私を導く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}遠い遠い呼び声よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}微笑むように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}歌うように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}響く風の音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}喜び悲しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}すべて抱いて歩いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}私の手と君の手を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}強く繋ぐもの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我已經到了打工的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老師請不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有唱歌還算拿手啊 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這一點和琥珀一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好聽哦 這孩子好像也不哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了小姐你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 再唱來聽一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多唱幾次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有舞台 到那邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收了大家好多禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 歌都唱了收就收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:19:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...那個那個...測驗呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 測驗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前半你盡做了些脫線的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半的那個火鍋也只是偶然的產物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌倒還湊合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你不是說了歌還湊合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前半太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?好過分!好過分啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很努力的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 離合格就差一點了 真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的老奶奶 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 唱歌很好聽的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再見到你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真的謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想對你道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子聽到媽媽以外的人唱歌會那麼開心還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過開心了沒多久很快就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您特意為我孫子唱了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻沒道謝就直接走了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌 真的很好聽哦 有機會再讓我聽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...是[瓶]吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 剛才老奶奶的感謝讓你逆轉成功了 測驗合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要就還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒受傷的心靈 把心的碎片裝滿這個瓶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也只是剛剛才拿到[瓶]而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花戶小鳩 你的願望是?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現願望需要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須收集受傷的心靈裝滿這個[瓶]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 真正的戰鬥現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走的路還遠得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 小鳩 會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑的傻呵呵的 你真的明白嗎 土鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好過分啊 我的名字是小鳩 花戶小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫土鳩就很對得起你 不樂意就叫你DABADA
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.32,0:22:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?DABADA...

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:08.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:16.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:24.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:33.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:43.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:50.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:54.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:24:02.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:06.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:11.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:15.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:28.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:08.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人們都是那麼想飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:16.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不過被重力所欺騙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:24.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其實誰都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:33.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那個孩子為什麼如此悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:43.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也許是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:46.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:50.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能對你說 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:54.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看見你的笑容 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:24:02.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來來往往中 變得愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:06.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:11.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:15.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:28.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜極而泣總是那麼不可思議

